article.headline: Army 59, Colgate 57
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. (AP) -- Jarell Brown scored 19 points, Doug Williams added 12 points and 12 rebounds and Army edged Colgate 59-57 in overtime in Patriot League basketball on Saturday. Kendall Chones scored 20 and grabbed 9 rebounds for the Raiders (11-12, 3-6). Kyle Roemer added 16 points. Alex Woodhouse had 8 points and 11 boards. The Black Knights (11-11, 4-4) trailed 25-23 at halftime in a game whose lead changed 13 times and which was tied nine times, including 52-52 at the end of regulation play.
